caption.title: Vital signs and age of macaques before and after ZIKV infection. Weight distribution per animal cohort.
caption.p: (A) Weight of rhesus macaques is expressed in kilograms (kg). (B) Age of rhesus macaques considered young adults. (C) Rectal temperature (in Celsius) was measured. Animals exposed to DENV 12 months before ZIKV infection are depicted in blue, while animals exposed to DENV 3 months before are in orange. Na√Øve animals are in black.
